globs:
alwaysApply: false
---

- Always keep responsiveness in mind throughout the development process
- Adopt a Mobile-First Strategy to ensure optimal experience on all devices
- Use Fluid Sizing instead of fixed values to allow layouts to adapt seamlessly
- Ensure Fluid Media, and use functions like clamp() for fluid typography to minimize reliance on media queries
